        <Parent_String>music boxes [300042659], mechanical instruments [300041725], musical instruments [300041620], sound devices by function [300205016], sound devices (equipment) [300387677], Sound Devices (hierarchy name) [300041619], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
